<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Longform Factory <%= versionLabel %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/app.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="dashboard-shell">
      <aside class="dashboard-sidebar compact-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-brand compact-brand">
          <div class="brand-mark">LF</div>
        </div>

        <nav class="sidebar-menu compact-menu">
          <a class="menu-item compact-item active" href="/" title="Dashboard">
            <span class="menu-dot"></span>
            <span class="compact-text">Dash</span>
          </a>
          <a class="menu-item compact-item" href="#create" title="New Workflow">
            <span class="menu-dot"></span>
            <span class="compact-text">New</span>
          </a>
          <a class="menu-item compact-item" href="#channels" title="Channels">
            <span class="menu-dot"></span>
            <span class="compact-text">Ch</span>
          </a>
          <a class="menu-item compact-item" href="#projects" title="Projects">
            <span class="menu-dot"></span>
            <span class="compact-text">List</span>
          </a>
        </nav>

        <section class="sidebar-note compact-note">
          <p class="eyebrow">핵심 흐름</p>
          <ul class="sidebar-list">
            <li>주제 선택</li>
            <li>소재 발굴</li>
            <li>대본 작성</li>
            <li>장면 생성</li>
            <li>렌더링</li>
            <li>업로드</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </aside>

      <main class="dashboard-main">
        <section class="hero-board">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">Longform 자동 공장</p>
            <h1>워크플로우 중심 제작 화면</h1>
            <p class="sub">Trior 계열 대시보드 방향처럼 한 화면에서 흐름과 상태를 바로 보게 구성했습니다.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-stats">
            <article class="stat-card accent">
              <span class="stat-label">버전</span>
              <strong><%= versionLabel %></strong>
            </article>
            <article class="stat-card">
              <span class="stat-label">채널 수</span>
              <strong><%= channels.length %></strong>
            </article>
            <article class="stat-card">
              <span class="stat-label">프로젝트 수</span>
              <strong><%= projects.length %></strong>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="dashboard-grid">
          <section class="dashboard-column main-column">
            <article class="dashboard-card" id="create">
              <div class="card-header">
                <div>
                  <p class="eyebrow">새 워크플로우</p>
                  <h2>프로젝트 만들기</h2>
                </div>
                <span class="pill">Auto + Manual</span>
              </div>

              <form class="form-grid dashboard-form" action="/projects" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <label>주제
                  <input type="text" name="topic" placeholder="예: 수면의 질을 높이는 습관" required />
                </label>

                <label>언어
                  <select name="language">
                    <option value="ko">한국어</option>
                    <option value="en">영어</option>
                    <option value="ja">일본어</option>
                  </select>
                </label>

                <label>톤
                  <input type="text" name="tone" value="정보형" />
                </label>

                <label>화면 비율
                  <select name="format">
                    <option value="portrait">세로형 9:16</option>
                    <option value="landscape">가로형 16:9</option>
                  </select>
                </label>

                <label>채널
                  <select name="channelId">
                    <option value="">선택 안 함</option>
                    <% channels.forEach((channel) => { %>
                      <option value="<%= channel.id %>"><%= channel.name %></option>
                    <% }) %>
                  </select>
                </label>

                <label>예약 시작
                  <input type="datetime-local" name="scheduledAt" />
                </label>

                <label class="wide">추가 지시
                  <input type="text" name="customPrompt" placeholder="예: 차분하고 신뢰감 있게" />
                </label>

                <label>스타일 레퍼런스
                  <input type="file" name="styleReference" accept="image/*" />
                </label>

                <label>BGM 파일
                  <input type="file" name="bgmFile" accept="audio/*" />
                </label>

                <label class="wide">워터마크
                  <input type="file" name="watermarkFile" accept="image/*" />
                </label>

                <div class="wide form-actions">
                  <button type="submit">워크플로우 시작</button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </article>

            <article class="dashboard-card" id="projects">
              <div class="card-header">
                <div>
                  <p class="eyebrow">프로젝트 목록</p>
                  <h2>최근 워크플로우</h2>
                </div>
                <span class="muted-caption">프로젝트 클릭 시 세부 워크플로우 화면으로 이동</span>
              </div>

              <div class="project-board">
                <% if (!projects.length) { %>
                  <div class="empty-board">
                    <strong>아직 프로젝트가 없습니다.</strong>
                    <p>위 입력 카드에서 새 워크플로우를 시작하면 좌측 단계형 편집 화면으로 이동합니다.</p>
                  </div>
                <% } %>

                <% projects.forEach((project) => { %>
                  <a class="project-tile" href="/projects/<%= project.id %>?step=topic">
                    <div>
                      <strong><%= project.topic %></strong>
                      <p><%= project.language %> · <%= project.tone %> · <%= project.format %></p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="badge <%= project.status %>"><%= project.status %></span>
                  </a>
                <% }) %>
              </div>
            </article>
          </section>

          <aside class="dashboard-column side-column">
            <article class="dashboard-card compact-card" id="channels">
              <div class="card-header">
                <div>
                  <p class="eyebrow">채널</p>
                  <h2>업로드 채널</h2>
                </div>
              </div>

              <form class="form-grid single-form" action="/channels" method="post">
                <label>채널 이름
                  <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="메인 유튜브 채널" />
                </label>

                <label>플랫폼
                  <input type="text" name="platform" value="youtube" />
                </label>

                <label>업로드 웹훅 URL
                  <input type="text" name="uploadWebhookUrl" placeholder="n8n webhook URL" />
                </label>

                <div class="form-actions">
                  <button type="submit">채널 저장</button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </article>

            <article class="dashboard-card compact-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <div>
                  <p class="eyebrow">워크플로우 상태</p>
                  <h2>진행 방식</h2>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="timeline-card">
                <div class="timeline-item done">
                  <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
                  <div>
                    <strong>주제 선택</strong>
                    <p>자동 초안과 수동 입력 혼합</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                  <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
                  <div>
                    <strong>대본 작성</strong>
                    <p>리서치 기반 자동 생성 후 직접 보정</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                  <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
                  <div>
                    <strong>장면/렌더</strong>
                    <p>장면별 재생성과 전체 렌더 분리</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
          </aside>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
